                        <interp inst="t18660611-name-523" type="given" value="FREDERICK"></interp>FREDERICK WYMAN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Police-sergeant</hi>, 24 W). After taking the prisoner on the last charge, I took off his boots and compared them with footmarks which I traced to the back of the prosecutrix's premises—they corresponded—I found the greater part of these things lying in the garden, and a portion in the timber yard, strewed all over the place.</p>
